⠀⠀⠯⣀⣈⣀⣈⣐⣲⣄⣄⣤⣴⣆⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣈⣛⡧⠀⠀⠀
                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                      
  Useful Logs
     Filename                                          Purpose            
    
  /var/account/acct                            process-level accounting
  
  /var/log/lastlog                             Logs each user’s most recent successful login time, and possibly the last unsuccessful login, too
(ask me about the command lastlog)    

    btmp (ask me about the command lastb)              Records bad login attempts

    secure                                            Messages generated from the syslog facility that require extra privacy      

    sulog                                                   Logs use of the su command
 
    utmp(x)
(ask me about the commands who and w)                Records each user currently logged in

    wtmp(x)                                          Provides a permanent record of each time a user logged in and out; also records system shutdowns and startups
(ask me about the command last)

  xferlog                                             Logs ftp access

  /var/log/secure /var/log/auth.log                   Messages generated from the syslog facility that require extra privacy 

